{"tid":1033343,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖雲達斯瀕出局 C朗變丁蟹 祖記股價大趺1成","createTime":"2019-02-23T05:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T03:04:23.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3dec7ba26363687fa86cce4bb0f237ed8e086256","tid":1033343,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20190223/photo/bkn-20190223005251509-0223_00882_001_01p.jpg?20190223045848\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20190223%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190223005251509-0223_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20190223045848&h=0260990d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利財經傳媒報道，祖雲達斯在歐聯16強首回合作客淨吞馬德里體育會兩蛋，瀕臨出局邊緣，連累祖記股價暴跌10%。 <br />\n<br />\n周三(20日)祖雲達斯股價收報1.45歐元，但球隊在歐聯輸波後，周四開市報價為1.29歐元，跌幅10.01%，之後回穩，周五收市報1.31歐元。 <br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯尚有主場次回合收復失地，假如成功翻身反勝晉級，股價自然回復舊觀甚至爆升，一旦出局，球會將至少損失1050萬歐元，其他周邊損失有待估算，股價有機會進一步受壓。"},{"pid":"ad143af55d81a31f3402764aa1562361671540f9","tid":1033343,"uid":58811,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"下場就熱血反勝兼戴帽"},{"pid":"40b45a63784dc03b608eeb17d5eaac2ab054bbd7","tid":1033343,"uid":165598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9ef1a577d331ceb8b8f969822356e9ca17b0aca","tid":1033343,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad143af55d81a31f3402764aa1562361671540f9","tid":1033343,"uid":58811,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"下場就熱血反勝兼戴帽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:41:17.000Z","msg":"黑哨都輸，無人幫到佢"},{"pid":"1cb5965bb41c6fdc940ecd6d88f7ee8da80c0c7f","tid":1033343,"uid":3454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ad143af55d81a31f3402764aa1562361671540f9","tid":1033343,"uid":58811,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"下場就熱血反勝兼戴帽"},"citedBy":1,"reply